urls.title: Alabama coronavirus maps and data: The latest numbers
urls.description: We're tracking where coronavirus cases are in Alabama in our COVID-19 dashboard.

text:
For the first time, #Alabama reports an increase of more than 1,000 cases of #COVID19 in a single day.

After four straight days of record numbers, the 7-day average is now at 724 cases per day.

https://t.co/nJGqz8Zh6m https://t.co/SN9XlRHkZC
